Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_extrac...n_output_ports(25.10)    timing_extrac...n_output_ports(25.10)

Name
       timing_extract_model_enable_combinational_arc_to_clock_source_on_out-
       put_ports

Syntax
       timing_extract_model_enable_combinational_arc_to_clock_source_on_out-
       put_ports

       {true | false}

       Default : false

       When  set  to true, the software models the combinational arc ending on
       an end point with the clock asserted on it.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

Related Information
              * "Extracting Timing Models" chapter in the Innovus User Guide.

